{"id":166062,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/明報-中日軍機釣島上空對峙/","date":"2011-07-08T06:00:17Z","modified":"2011-07-08T06:00:17Z","title":"明報 | 中日軍機釣島上空對峙","content":"<div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/shim.gif\" alt=\"推\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\"> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p>【明報專訊】中國國防部昨日證實，中日軍機曾在釣魚島上空對峙。據日本防衛省聯合參謀部稱，中國兩架軍機7月4日一度飛近距釣魚島領空60公里處，日本航空自衛隊從那霸基地緊急出動F-15戰機攔截。中國國防部新聞事務局官員昨日證實，日方軍用艦機對中方正常海空行動長時間、近距離跟蹤監視，極易導致雙方的誤解、誤判。他並指日方飛機近年在東海針對中國的偵巡力度不斷加大，希望日方停止有關危險活動，避免意外事故發生。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/shim.gif\" alt=\"推\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[87